description: Influencers who specialize in fitness, gym routines, and wellness.

guidelines.products: Gym wear (e.g., leggings, sports bras, tank tops), branded water bottles, resistance bands, protein powders.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Basic (basic workout plans), Premium (advanced routines + nutrition), Elite (1-on-1 coaching, personalized plans).

description: Influencers focused on reviewing and showcasing tech products and gadgets.

guidelines.products: Branded tech accessories (e.g., phone cases, laptop stickers, earbuds), DIY tech kits.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Basic (early video access), Advanced (ad-free content, Q&A sessions), Expert (exclusive reviews, beta testing opportunities).

description: Influencers who cook, review restaurants, and showcase food trends.

guidelines.products: Recipe books, branded cooking utensils, gourmet food kits, branded water bottles
guidelines.membershipTiers: Standard (exclusive recipes), Premium (virtual cooking classes), Platinum (monthly gourmet ingredient boxes, 1-on-1 culinary coaching).

description: Influencers advocating for environmental causes and green living.

guidelines.products: Reusable bags, eco-friendly household products, branded stainless steel straws.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Green (eco-tip newsletters), Super Green (eco-friendly DIY projects, product discounts), Ultra Green (personalized sustainability plans, exclusive webinars).

description: Influencers who set or showcase the latest fashion trends.

guidelines.products: Exclusive clothing line drops, fashion accessories, digital look-books.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Basic (seasonal fashion tips), Stylish (virtual styling sessions, early access to line drops), Elite (personal shopping assistance, exclusive meet-and-greets).

description: Influencers who travel to exotic locations and showcase travel tips, tricks, and locales.

guidelines.products: Branded travel gear (e.g., backpacks, travel pouches), photo presets, travel journals.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Explorer (travel tips newsletter), Adventurer (exclusive travel videos, discounts on affiliated travel brands), Nomad (itinerary planning, 1-on-1 travel coaching).

description: Influencers who specialize in crafting, DIY projects, and creative arts.

guidelines.products: DIY kits, crafting tools, digital tutorial booklets.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Crafter (monthly DIY ideas), Artisan (exclusive crafting webinars, discount on products), Master (personalized project guidance, community features).

description: Influencers who give advice on parenting, child care, and related topics.

guidelines.products: Branded child care products (e.g., bibs, baby carriers), e-books on parenting, children's storybooks.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Parent (monthly parenting tips), Super Parent (webinars, product discounts), Ultimate Parent (personalized consultations, exclusive community forums).

description: Influencers offering guidance on personal finance, investments, and budgeting.

guidelines.products: Financial planners, e-books on finance, budgeting apps/tools.
guidelines.membershipTiers: Budgeter (monthly finance newsletters), Investor (investment tips, webinar access), Wealth Builder (1-on-1 finance coaching, exclusive tools).

description: Influencers who play, review, or analyze video games, especially competitive esports titles.

guidelines.products: Branded gaming accessories (e.g., mousepads, headsets), exclusive in-game skins, merch (t-shirts, posters).
guidelines.membershipTiers: Gamer (early video access), Pro Gamer (exclusive gameplay sessions, ad-free content), Elite Gamer (1-on-1 game coaching, tournament access).
